Wild Islands Zanzibar 
Zanzibar is a land of giants. Isolated from mainland Africa these islands harbour some of the most unique animals with many being the largest found anywhere in the world. From giant snails to the largest shark on earth, the whale shark they dwarf their mainland cousins. But when nightfall's on the island one the of the biggest creepy crawlies reveals itself, this animal needs to be seen to be believed.
